  "subject": "[Blocked by: CPS-2730 (Refactor docker-compose structure)]Update DMI plugin CSITs if needed to use healthchecks",
  "commit_message": "[Blocked by: CPS-2730 (Refactor docker-compose structure)]Update DMI plugin CSITs if needed to use healthchecks\n\n- Updated healthcheck in docker-compose.yml.\n- Ensured curl is used properly to check SDNC readiness via the HealthCheck API.\n- Added error handling to print \"SDNC not ready\" if the response is not 200.\n- Improved debugging by allowing logs to indicate health check failures.\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2646\nChange-Id: I1b7757fbb529022198c5a41352c2a8b1a3b9da33\nSigned-off-by: sourabh_sourabh <sourabh.sourabh@est.tech>\n",
